ustration or even rage.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375610/extras/dbea6c38877715e03964d7217499baf3.poster.avif?t=1690435535\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375610/extras/dbea6c38877715e03964d7217499baf3.webm?t=1690435535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375610/extras/dbea6c38877715e03964d7217499baf3.mp4?t=1690435535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
